{"data":[{"id":560564723,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9120318b7c0d42660b8a4913bb830a1c","url_token":"yi-ming-46-88","name":"佚名","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-45507be83e0901ee574e186de9398041_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-45507be83e0901ee574e186de9398041_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/9120318b7c0d42660b8a4913bb830a1c","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560564723","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-549c3c4539d80cc564e11f0463f1d50b_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545868847,"updated_time":1545869487,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-549c3c4539d80cc564e11f0463f1d50b_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2248\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-299eac7a014bca61c0a783dff6b65563_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-549c3c4539d80cc564e11f0463f1d50b_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='2248'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2248\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-299eac7a014bca61c0a783dff6b65563_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-549c3c4539d80cc564e11f0463f1d50b_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-549c3c4539d80cc564e11f0463f1d50b_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e作为一个高中生 我并不觉得你可以搞得出这玩意儿....\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们初中数学老师是暨大毕业的研究生，数学系。他曾经跟我们提过这个猜想，然后他告诉我们，只有真正出身数学系的才知道这玩意儿有多难，需要的理论基础不是一个高中生可以掌握的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，如果您真的证明出来了并且得到学术界承认，当我没说，我真心钦佩。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果没有，希望题主放下这些不切实际的东西，认真学习高中的各科知识，希望可以在好的学府和你成为校友。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e图是我问了老师的\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560564463,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c9e71c7ee876ac6bc11fe0e08790910f","url_token":"15931679878","name":"芋小喵Sunny","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6e005a4e2dc29df641d3fe22ec2d1179_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6e005a4e2dc29df641d3fe22ec2d1179_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c9e71c7ee876ac6bc11fe0e08790910f","user_type":"people","headline":"学生党\u0026amp;爱撸猫撸松鼠\u0026amp;almost理想主义者","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560564463","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545868814,"updated_time":1545868814,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e首先怀疑这件事情的真实性。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看头像和敷衍的个人简介，以及昵称直接就是一个“证明”，我怀疑这可能又是一个什么营销事件，要么就是没有实质成果单纯的哗众取宠。当然，关于昵称起成“证明”，题主想要刻意突出重点也不是不可能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e即便此事属实，我也十分怀疑这个证明的正确性，极有可能是民科。毕竟题主作为高中生知识水平有限，也许能够 想通 哥德巴赫猜想，但实际证明要求绝对的严谨，是未经过训练的人难以想象到的。正如他老师所说，他的竞赛教练表示，这是一篇浮于表面的证明。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 以及看题主的提问，证明哥德巴赫猜想能否保送清北，我真的怀疑此人是不是过于渴望“天才少年”的光环，高考走不通，就想着搞个大新闻火一把，听不进别人的意见，自命不凡。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e学术这种事情，尤其是自然科学类，多学点东西，多听听前辈的意见，一般不会错2333\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以及如果这件事属实，只能说，题主确实有很强的数学天赋，但仅靠天赋是很难创造出来什么的，不如沉下心来好好学点东西，好好修炼吧。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560561322,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3fe91dcc805cb2be29b74a8f98e84087","url_token":"fengdu-46","name":"xiaolaistyle","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-64c22d36e4c6bf5829728e0d13642887_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-64c22d36e4c6bf5829728e0d13642887_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3fe91dcc805cb2be29b74a8f98e84087","user_type":"people","headline":"控制科学与工程的菜鸟","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560561322","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545868144,"updated_time":1545868144,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e还啥清北数学系，直接菲尔茨奖了呀！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560551700,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b7113ba92b40f2c9514f32ab0a7fc597","url_token":"wen-bo-liang-29","name":"是菲菲er呀","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4b3328ee24c1e87c9c7e330205ed84e0_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4b3328ee24c1e87c9c7e330205ed84e0_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b7113ba92b40f2c9514f32ab0a7fc597","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy